  "body": "<div align=\"center\">\n\n![Fresh Weapons & Tools Compat Title Image](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/184974fc98891afebfeed52260932db1a5e6b78a.png)\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/modpack/elysium-days\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n  <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fyoncle/Elysium-Days/main/ed_badge.png\" alt=\"As seen in Elysium Days\" width=\"200\">\n</a>\n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n## 📜 ABOUT\n\nThis **Add-on** for [Fresh Weapons & Tools](https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/fresh-weapons-and-tools) provides compatibility for some mods that add more tools and weapons to the game.\n\n</div>\n<br>\n\n### Compatibility List\n\n<table>\n\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/fFEIiSDQ/e9f5f66fa3b67e54acb91258a1428d68311c58bc_96.webp\" alt=\"Supplementaries\" width=\"50\" height=\"auto\"></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/supplementaries\"><b>Supplementaries</b></a></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/2HaoWnJc/00e0637dcbad2d8c0d06ea4d178488f831d30925_96.webp\" alt=\"Tokimi's Toolshed\" width=\"50\" height=\"auto\"></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/tokimistoolshed\"><b>Tokimi's Toolshed</b></a></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/F0yI8Qcm/cad8041b91b9c19481d32da59e0e183302eba7d3.gif\" alt=\"Obsidian Equipment Reworked\" width=\"50\" height=\"auto\"></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/obsidian-equipment-reworked\"><b>Obsidian Equipment Reworked</b></a></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/fnAffV0n/be8023f374038c6bd8a52a0e5b2cbc4eb1a37746_96.webp\" alt=\"Deeper and Darker\" width=\"50\" height=\"auto\"></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/deeperdarker\"><b>Deeper and Darker</b></a></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/18b8084ccca942eaf388e78c5589caac6d9f8636.webp\" alt=\"Medieval Weapons\" width=\"50\" height=\"auto\"></td>\n<td><a href=\"https: